token_info.description: Beauty is in the eye of the beholder.  This WebGL composition will be built differently for each viewer.  Parameters such as colors, speed, size, arrangement and color sequence will be taken from your Tezos address.  If you are not connected, my creator address will be taken to create the composition.  There are over 8,000,000 possible unique combinations but this piece is limited to 500 unique outcomes..
